Q=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8088864?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62","html_url":"https://github.com/hankliu62","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"open_issues":17,"closed_issues":0,"state":"open","created_at":"2024-03-20T03:36:14Z","updated_at":"2024-04-19T04:10:46Z","due_on":null,"closed_at":null},"comments":0,"created_at":"2024-04-08T07:49:28Z","updated_at":"2024-04-08T07:49:28Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"`position: sticky;` 是一个有趣且强大的 CSS 属性，它可以让元素在滚动时表现出“粘性”的效果，即当元素滚动到指定位置时固定在屏幕上。这个属性的主要限制包括：\r\n\r\n1. **兼容性问题**：尽管大多数现代浏览器都支持 `position: sticky;`，但在某些旧版浏览器或移动端浏览器上可能存在兼容性问题。因此，在使用时需要考虑向后兼容性，并可能需要提供替代方案。\r\n\r\n2. **定位上下文**：`position: sticky;` 元素的粘性效果是相对于其最近的具有滚动机制的祖先元素（即滚动容器）来定位的。如果没有滚动容器，或者滚动容器的高度不足以触发粘性效果，那么 `position: sticky;` 将不会生效。\r\n\r\n3. **性能问题**：在某些情况下，使用 `position: sticky;` 可能会导致性能问题，特别是在大量元素同时具有粘性效果时。这可能会导致页面滚动时的卡顿或性能下降。\r\n\r\n4. **表现不一致**：在某些情况下，不同浏览器或设备上的 `position: sticky;` 的表现可能会有所不同，导致一些意外的结果。因此，在使用时需要进行充分的测试和调试，以确保所需的效果能够在各种环境下得到正确地展示。\r\n\r\n考虑到以上限制，开发者在使用 `position: sticky;` 属性时需要谨慎，并且在必要时提供替代方案以确保良好的用户体验。\r\n","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/585/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocke